	other regulatory authorities. If we modify our current
	manufacturing processes, the FDA and other regulatory
	authorities will require us to demonstrate that the material
	produced from the modified or new process or facility is
	equivalent to the material used in the clinical trials or
	products previously approved. Any such modifications to the
	manufacturing process or supply may not achieve or maintain
	compliance with the applicable regulatory


